snippet.title: "Game-Kun: Input Challenge" Gameplay Reveal.
snippet.description:
(Launching Feb 8th 2021!)
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1283660/GameKun_Input_Challenge/

Game-Kun: Input Challenge is a reaction-based hiscore mini game. Test your reflexes and input skills with your gamepad. Unlock skins and other characters to enhance the fun! Can you clear the challenge course and compete for the ultimate Hi-score in Infinite Mode?

Twitter: https://twitter.com/KasaOnIdeas

Facebook :https://www.facebook.com/KasaOnIdeas
